  "detailed_description": "As Shmandalf the wizard, herd your wayward flock of sheep to safety while fending off the monsters that prey on them with your wizardly prowess! Manage your farm in between adventures to earn gold and acquire unique spells and upgrades on your path to sheep herding supremacy.<br><br>---<br><br><strong>**A Mystically Magical Shepherd Experience**</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Put your sorcerous skills to the test as you defend your herd from monsters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/eefa8b229c654d4cb08558c8fdf4fb44.apng?t=1756139878\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/eefa8b229c654d4cb08558c8fdf4fb44.poster.avif?t=1756139878\" class=\"bb_img\" width=488 height=148 /></picture></span><br><br><br></li><li>Guide your sheep through treacherous terrains on your otherworldly odyssey through a variety of environments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/f3c1c2457faa0144384af2a0d5e40cf6.apng?t=1756139878\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/f3c1c2457faa0144384af2a0d5e40cf6.poster.avif?t=1756139878\" class=\"bb_img\" width=510 height=247 /></picture></span><br><br><br></li><li>Power up your spells for everything from combat, to sheep herding, to farming.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/ae20b47d8d9f8623ec7b9fd6000d5074.avif?t=1756139878\" width=424 height=205 /></span><br><br>---<br><br><strong>**Master the Arcane Art of Sheep Farming**</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your sheep farm and expand your flocks and crops to mighty proportions.<br></li><li>Raise your sheep for wool, cultivate your garden, then haul them off to the farmer-wizard’s market for gold and assorted arcane goods.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/3edd7075516f5c32ac4a699e0edcef49.apng?t=1756139878\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/3edd7075516f5c32ac4a699e0edcef49.poster.avif?t=1756139878\" class=\"bb_img\" width=468 height=214 /></picture></span><br><br>---<br><br><strong>**Mandatory Fishing Game**</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wizards fish too.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/e9368629b07f58f60ea3e9bf8e147b83.poster.avif?t=1756139878\" width=568 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480210/extras/e9368629b07f58f60ea3e9bf8e147b83.webm?t=1756139878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
